---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import profileImage from '../assets/about-profile.png';
---

<Layout title="About">
	<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start mb-20">
			<div class="relative">
				<div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 relative group shadow-2xl">
					<Image 
						src={profileImage} 
						alt="SpAi-C Profile" 
						class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
					/>
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-space-black/60 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
				</div>
				<!-- Decorative elements -->
				<div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-8">
				<div>
					<span class="text-accent font-oxanium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-sm mb-2 block">Origin Story</span>
					<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-brand mb-6 leading-tight">SpAi-C</h1>
					<div class="space-y-6 text-white/70 font-inter leading-relaxed text-lg">
						<p>
							SpAi-C is a fictional digital space pop artist whose everyday life in London blends seamlessly with an imagined universe among the stars.
						</p>
						<p>
							Her songs drift between reality and escapism, inspired by quiet commutes, late-night thoughts, cups of tea, and those moments when looking up at the night sky makes life's problems feel just a little smaller. Space isn't a destination—it's a place to think, breathe, and find perspective.
						</p>
						<p>
							Every release is another transmission from that world, where the ordinary and the extraordinary quietly overlap. Some stories begin on a London street, others somewhere among the stars, and many exist somewhere in between. Whether she's writing about gravity, connection, loneliness, hope, or simply trying to make it through another day, SpAi-C reminds us that we're all searching for our place in the universe.
						</p>
						<p>
							SpAi-C is an original fictional character created as a music and visual art project using modern AI creative tools. She isn't presented as a real person, but as a character whose stories invite listeners to escape, reflect, and see the world from a slightly different perspective.
						</p>
						<p class="italic text-white/90">
							So, wherever you are, thanks for tuning in. Your next transmission is about to begin.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="flex space-x-6 pt-4">
					<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@spai_c" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-accent hover:border-accent transition-all">
						<span class="sr-only">TikTok</span>
