					</a>
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/spaicmusic/" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-accent hover:border-accent transition-all">
						<span class="sr-only">Instagram</span>
